<br>
Rules for these events -- pretty open.  But you MUST have a true public signup sheet.  These aren't events to invite a bunch of your friends, these are PUBLIC events.<br>
<br>
To that end, I'd like people to post to this thread if they would like to schedule and host a public event.  Please include your email address -- or else email me as admin@innoruuk.com.  What I'll do is change the password for &quot;public events&quot; and email the password to the first host, so that he/she can schedule an event.<br>
<br>
This person should pick as near a date as reasonable -- don't go making it 6 months away or anything like that.<br>
<br>
We weren't clear during the meeting how much moderation Inny.com is supposed to do on this.  I don't think I'm supposed to exercise much authority over who the hosts are, although if I were going to do so, I'd be picking people I trusted to run good raids.<br>
<br>
My personal desire is that only people who have been to the planes numerous times in the past and are confident of their ability to organize a complex raid volunteer to host these.<br>
<br>
So, who wants to hold a raid?<br>
